{"tid":704931,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【世界盃】還原事件真相 陳奕迅遭外籍球迷無禮對待","createTime":"2018-06-16T16:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T10:19:37.000Z","uid":188396,"like":540,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"8e2e7bd20fa18b1c56719d9f9c865c5163db5474","tid":704931,"uid":188396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T16:58:23.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅（Eason）專誠飛往俄羅斯欣賞世界盃揭幕戰，據知Eason今次獲廣告商邀請到現場睇賽事，但有報道指現場有網民或球迷認得Eason，便用手機影他，不過卻觸怒Eason，Eason嬲到舉中指。<br />\n<br />\n不過事件有另一版本，Eason經理人甘菁菁，接受《明報》訪問時表示，因為當時好多內地Fans發現Eason，更有球迷走過去偷拍，甚至向Eason湧過去，湊巧有外籍男球迷被撞倒，加上當時已開波，Eason為免騷擾到其他球迷，索性坐落下一行控制場面，並叫大家不要偷拍，也不要湧前，但該外籍球迷知道因為是Eason才惹起混亂，便舉中指兼爆粗鬧Eason，Eason有感對方沒有禮貌，所以憤而回應。甘菁菁又說：「這位外國人不應該這樣無禮對我們中國人。」<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1529058121214&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180615\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1529058121214%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180615&d=SN79dnOdyUqSvXT8OLBezS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=086e2d40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1529058121214%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180615&h=825ff3a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1529058121214&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180615</a><br />\n<br />\n係上個post係咁鬧佢嘅人可唔可以出黎回應下<br />\nChild登仔啲炒車技術都幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ee064a3d2962751950a1248546b82062acda33","tid":704931,"uid":188396,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T16:59:03.000Z","msg":"講緊呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50cc07cd324f4d77ce2f1149270383a70ea339e0","tid":704931,"uid":188396,"like":3,"dislike":2,